competitive_positioning.competitive_moat: Technical differentiation through WebAssembly integration with proven runtime concepts from Go/Erlang

competitive_advantages: Proven concurrency model from Erlang/Go heritage
competitive_vulnerabilities: Small team size limits development speed
Competing against established runtimes with large ecosystems

key_risks: Small team executing complex technical vision

strengths: Addresses real performance needs in growing market segments
Novel technical approach combining proven concepts
Targets high-value use cases like gaming and real-time communications
concerns: Market education required for WebAssembly server-side adoption
